2.	Tracer: 125Iodine labelled IGF-1 (HPLC grade) in phosphate buffer with bovine albumin and azide (<0.1%)

4.	Zero calibrator in phosphate buffer with ovalbumin and gentamycin

6.	Pre-treatment Solution containing HCl 0.1N

8.	Wash solution (TRIS-HCl) 
9.	Controls (1 or 2) in human serum with thymol
